Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Messages deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:56.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:59.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:04.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:08.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Miyamura-senpai. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:10.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,W-What, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:16.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan is sleeping right now. Can you keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see him at once! There's something important I need to tell him. Let me see Hirono-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't allowed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be with Onii-chan after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Hello, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's for lunch today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:40.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious. I always enjoy Renji-kun's bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What score would you give it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to score it. It was very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, can you teach me how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:14.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Onee-chan is learning to cook, so I want to be able to cook something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:18.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Well, why don't we try something simple for starters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:19.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:30.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is in an area without service and cannot be connected-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:43.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, it's a medial something something collateral something something injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of "somethings".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's because of how the name is written.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least remember the name of the injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In order to relieve the pain, try not to move too much and apply plenty of ice."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I guess you won't be able to play basketball for a while then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, what about practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The same as always, though I really should rest instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It probably would be a good idea to slow down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:18.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you have to rest your leg as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll keep you company for a bit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl spent a lot of time looking at the painting."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:45.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking at the boy in the painting gave her a strange feeling."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:49.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to marry him.' For some reason or another she thought about that."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In a book, she found out a lot about marriage."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:59.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Inside, it was written that it was important how people lived their lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:04.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl was interested in how the ideals of marriage worked and carefully studied it."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, have you thought about what career to go into?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's the career survey to fill out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, at the moment I haven't really decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, you'd be great if you became a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:22.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your stories are so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:27.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough being a novelist though. Perhaps it just won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:34.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I read what you write, Chihiro, I can't seem to come up with anything better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:37.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I just don't have the right talent for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:45.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't talent that is important, but the ability to try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you taught me, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:57.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'll soon be able to finish my novel even though I always believed that it was impossible and wanted to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can't remember anything after thirteen hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and even though what happened when I was twelve keeps coming back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you showed me there was always a way to make it, Renji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So please do not ever give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:17.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you have a dream, please do your best and don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:32.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This part was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:53.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just want things back the way they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to live freely no matter where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:01.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is neither a place to return to nor a place to come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:10.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To be trapped in the ruins of the past isn't a good thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:16.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know where that warmth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:24.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you embrace these wonderful memories, you'll never choose the wrong path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Such a faraway memory I can't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But you are starting to remember, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:35.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it would've been better if we never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:40.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If we didn't meet, I wouldn't have tried to remember this warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is the girl Chihiro doing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, little by little. Just recently, her memory has started to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle happening is an unrelated matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:02.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, there is no possibility that such a thing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:08.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What we have is what is expected, unexpected, and what one has done. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Have you remembered what I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:13.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is in an area without service and-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-B's Hirono Hiro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:34.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-D's Miyamura Miyako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:37.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,After school, please come to the guidance counselor's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"What are you going to do about the career survey?" they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The same with Miyamura-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She ditched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:53.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Wouldn't it be better to concentrate less on work and more on your studies after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And maybe I should do some work on the rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:01.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! After this is over with, why don't we go out somewhere? I-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:02.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Shindou Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm doing what I can about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The run is finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:16.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll give it a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime this week, I'll bring over a draft copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:30.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The run was finished and they want something else to be serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is a chance after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You just said earlier you were going to take a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I said no, there wouldn't be another opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:44.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For a newcomer like me, if any kind of chance comes along, I have to take a stab at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Well, so you'll do whatever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities. If I don't move around my body is going to get weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Didn't you say you were going to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, even though you aren't getting better, you aren't going to stop either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you really injure your leg, you won't be able to play basketball anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well if it gets worse, you won't be able to write manga anymore, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:06.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do this, some other artist is going to steal my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think I understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you can't possibly do anything with that injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Was I asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:30.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How much time has passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,About how long was I asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:38.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, it was about five minutes, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you just stopped because you were tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No I wasn't. I'm not tired at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Things are okay then I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:01.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what an idiot. Jumping back into work even when he is lacking attendance, what is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:05.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you request for him to plan in advance, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan, why did you take up basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:09.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:14.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to blow past the operation and set up for the shot is a real rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:23.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you take a shot at the right time and place that touches your heart, it gives you a great feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the same for Hirono too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:34.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,He's always trying to move ahead, so his path is one that's more difficult than ours you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But he's still an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You really are oblivious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping in the middle like that is a cheap shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You see, when trying to film a wild animal in their natural habitat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you can't interfere with what they are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you cannot get footage in its natural state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I cut into the conversation, it'll just be interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't equate people with the behavior of animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:11.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't give me that know-it-all talk, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I understand though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With the camera's viewfinder, I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:14.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:19.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In the middle of a meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,11:50. I arrived at the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Four minutes later, Renji-kun showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We ate lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:43.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The bento consisted of fried halibut, Japanese-style salad and for dessert, strawberry jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:48.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was delicious. I always enjoy Renji-kun's bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"What score would you give it today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:54.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no need to score it. It was very good."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:59.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time, can you teach me how to cook?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:02.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, why don't we try something simple for starters?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Working on your studies this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you already do your reading before you went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everything except the summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Summary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:39.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The diary I keep is only a summary. With the things that I had fun with, I write that "I had fun".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:47.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This way, how I had fun or what feelings I experienced won't all disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you are writing down your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,While reading this, I can remember every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This way I will be able to remember the events of the previous thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:02.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This way I will remember what happened when I met with Renji-kun this afternoon and everything up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll be writing until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:05.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And you will continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the time I spent with Renji-kun to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I am an ordinary girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:18.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? There isn't much time after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to continue! Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason to continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, this won't help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:37.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Give it back, I beg you! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:41.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of it... Inside of it my Renji-kun is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That just now... I will never forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for that disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What was it like the first time we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:20.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to paint this important memory in my heart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We were gazing at the sky I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:30.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, you looked deeply into the sky that day. It was a mysterious feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That day... was definitely like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:41.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But looking ahead towards the future is a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:49.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun, I... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Could we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:02.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if it isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:12.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that it's the end if we don't. I was just thinking that I wanted to try it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't... possible, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:19.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:51.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The next day, the girl married. She wore a dress she found in the castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:57.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"In her head, to the words, 'Will you accept the vow of matrimony?' she answered yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:03.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Then, she touched lips with the man in the painting. It was oily."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:08.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"She then took some flowers to use as a bouquet and tossed it."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:13.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"A feast was properly prepared. It was a party to some degree."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:19.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"But due to the tightness of the dress around her waist, there was much that was leftover."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:27.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"The girl took the bouquet, dress, and the leftover food and tossed it over a cliff like garbage and slept."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,"Thus the wedding ended."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:35.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:37.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:37.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:38.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me, didn't you? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is Chihiro... all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:49.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lot of strain, lack of sleep and emotional stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:54.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,All these factors that were built up inside her disappeared after she was at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:58.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I tried, she wouldn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since the time limit has passed, I let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:06.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:28.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do I look older?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with my eye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan? Where is Kei-oneechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Hiro-oniichan? What happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.21,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chihiro! You've already-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why... What has happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro, do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:04.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:20.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She will always be a twelve-year-old who can't remember anything past thirteen hours of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:05.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:10.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:14.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:16.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:18.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What, you actually remembered me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:25.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? You got me all worried when I couldn't get a hold of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on your cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:29.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:30.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:34.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disappeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:39.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To the ones who don't know pain, it is a more painful tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1}ef - a tale of memories:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Forget Me Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
